  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00716', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作師法為規範社工工作之資格取得、執業、社會工作師事務所等相關事宜進行規範之法令。下列 敘述何者錯誤？', '["社會工作師執行業務時，應撰製社會工作紀錄，其紀錄應由執業之機關（構）、團體、事務所保存。 紀錄保存年限不得少於五年", "社會工作師及專科社會工作師執業，應接受繼續教育，並每六年提出完成繼續教育證明文件，辦理執 業執照更新", "申請設立社會工作師事務所之社會工作師，須執行第12條所訂之業務五年以上，並得有工作證明者， 始得為之", "社會工作師公會之組織區域依現有之行政區域劃分，分為直轄市公會、縣（市）公會，並得設社會工 作師公會全國聯合會"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00717', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '在許多社政法規中皆明定為推行相關工作，應編列預算或設置基金。下列那一個社政法規中明定，緩起 訴處分金是基金來源？', '["家庭暴力防治法", "兒童及少年性剝削防制條例", "長期照顧服務法", "中高齡者及高齡者就業促進法"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00718', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國社會工作師法明定「社會工作師倫理守則」，是由下列何者所訂定？', '["全國社會工作師公會聯合會", "衛生福利部", "立法院", "內政部"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00719', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國就業保險法對於失業給付申請人離職辦理本保險退保時已年滿45歲或領有社政主管機關核發之身心 障礙證明者，最長發給幾個月？', '["9個月", "12個月", "15個月", "18個月"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00720', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '我國勞動基準法所定義之「平均工資」是指，計算事由發生之當日前幾個月內所得工資總額除以該期間 之總日數所得之金額？', '["3個月內", "4個月內", "5個月內", "6個月內"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00721', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關就業保險法相關規定之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["受僱於二個以上雇主者，得擇一參加本保險", "本保險之給付包括喪葬給付、失業給付、職業訓練生活津貼、育嬰留職停薪津貼", "本法所稱非自願離職，指被保險人因投保單位關廠、遷廠、休業、解散、破產宣告離職", "失業給付按申請人離職辦理本保險退保之當月起前六個月平均月投保薪資百分之六十按月發給"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00722', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關育嬰留職停薪津貼之相關敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["請領資格條件之一為被保險人之就業保險年資合計滿六個月以上", "請領資格條件之一為在被保險人之子女滿三歲前", "請領資格條件之一為被保險人在依性別工作平等法之規定，辦理育嬰留職停薪期間", "民國110年7月1日起政府加發20%育嬰留職停薪薪資補助，與育嬰留職停薪津貼合併發給"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 42, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00723', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-1f300fa3', 'sub-elementary-64311456-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依就業保險法之規定，領取失業給付者，應於辦理失業再認定時，至少提供幾次以上求職紀錄，始得繼 續請領？', '["一次", "二次", "三次", "四次"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "702601c709e6", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1ca8c696a53d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0301", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社政法規大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
